@NorwegianJan Hi! The check in closes 1 hour before the departure. Airports usually open their bag drops between 2-4 hours before the departure. I recommend that you always make it to the airport as early as you can as it can take longer time than expected at the airport.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Blackblade Hi, if our website cannot offer you an upgrade for your flights with a Star alliance airline, then unfortunately it is not something we are able to assist you with manually. You can always check if you are able to upgrade your flight at the boarding desk.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Tryall_ Hi! When you fly within Scandinavia you won't need a facemask. However when you fly to, from and within Europe, USA or Asia, you will be required to wear a facemask and will be denied boarding if you don't wear a mask our flights within the specified area.
Kind regards, Rebecka
